      "acceptanceCriteria": "The validation experiments must represent the intended COU sufficiently to support the regulatory submission decision.",
      "rationale": "Validation activities directly replicate the ASTM F1717 test protocol specified in the COU. The non-cannulated 7.5 mm screw tested is the same design submitted for regulatory review. Cross-laboratory validation at FDA OSEL and DePuy Synthes strengthens generalizability. Validation activities judged sufficient to support the Accepted decision."
    }
